    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm just really worried about taking all these chemicals for no reason if the infection is already gone. it feels like a lot for my body to process for another week. is there any way i can just taper off or skip a few days to see how it goes? i don't want to overdo it if it's not needed anymore.",
