    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i've heard that taking a long course of antibiotics like this can actually mess up your gut health and kill off all the good bacteria. if the infection is already gone, isn't it more harmful to keep taking them than to just stop? seems like a waste of medicine and bad for my microbiome if i don't actually need them anymore.",
